1ï¸âƒ£ Detect Cycle in a Linked List (LeetCode #141)
Problem: Determine if a linked list has a cycle (i.e., a node points back to a previous node).

âœ… Code:
python
Copy
Edit
def has_cycle(head):
    slow = head
    fast = head

    while fast and fast.next:
        slow = slow.next
        fast = fast.next.next

        if slow == fast:
            return True  # They met, so there is a cycle

    return False  # fast reached the end â†’ no cycle

